HEAD: Runed Circlet<br>
FINGER 1: Velium Jasper Ring (Or +5 RF ring)<br>
FINGER 2: Velium Jasper Ring (Or +5 RF ring)<br>
WRISTS 1: Chipped Bone Bracelet (Or Vox bracer)<br>
WRISTS 2: Chipped Bone Bracelet<br>
ARMS: Ulthork Arms (Elder Spiritists Vambraces when I get some)<br>
HANDS: Spit Paw Gloves <br>
SHOULDER: Braided Ivy Cords <br>
CHEST: Foreman's Tunic<br>
BACK: Mammoth Hide Cloak <br>
